{"tid":533661,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"北京市政協名單出爐　鄭泳舜、管浩鳴首次獲任","createTime":"2018-01-19T04:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T04:16:57.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"80ca03eb829ce490ff1e9dfc0b6f59ed502b6181","tid":533661,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:16:57.000Z","msg":"北京市第十三屆政協委員名單今天公布，參加九西補選的民建聯鄭泳舜、聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴、郭炳聯兒子新地執董郭基泓等，均首次成功躋身北京市政協之列。<br />\n<br />\n第十三屆北京市政協共有759人，不少香港人均以「特別邀請人士」的身份上榜。從名單可見，鄭泳舜、管浩鳴、郭基泓都是首次做北京市政協。英皇集團主席楊受成兒子楊政龍、民建聯立法會議員劉國勳，同樣是首次當選。<br />\n<br />\n信德集團董事總經理何超瓊、信和集團執行董事黃永光、恆基地產副主席李家誠等人成功連任。李嘉誠次子、電盈主席李澤楷則榜上無名。<br />\n<br />\n鄭泳舜早前已報名參與立法會九龍西補選，料與勝出民主派初選的姚松炎對撼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90-%E9%84%AD%E6%B3%B3%E8%88%9C-%E7%AE%A1%E6%B5%A9%E9%B3%B4%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E7%8D%B2%E4%BB%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2588%2590-%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E8%2588%259C-%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25B3%25B4%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BB%25BB%2F&d=gOWvjm7v2wDT3Waua6LgiL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1323f0fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2588%2590-%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E8%2588%259C-%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25B3%25B4%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BB%25BB%2F&h=29c61b6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90-%E9%84%AD%E6%B3%B3%E8%88%9C-%E7%AE%A1%E6%B5%A9%E9%B3%B4%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E7%8D%B2%E4%BB%BB/</a>"}]}